<P>
99 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
A DIFFERENT MORAL STANDARD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Kevin Weston wants us to judge a group of individuals on a different moral 
standard because they are African Americans ("Kids Weren't Laughing at 
Holocaust, Just Movie," Feb. 28).This is an injustice to all Americans. 
</P>
<P>
 Their behavior was inappropriate and unkind. This was a group of teen-agers 
that behaved poorly. 
</P>
<P>
 JOHN N. CALLAS 
</P>
<P>
 Oceanside 
</P>
<P>
 * 
</P>
<P>
 When "Menace II Society" was released, did we hear of Latinos laughing because 
they weren't visible on the screen? Did Asians and Native Americans laugh at 
other movies because of hardships they had to go through? 
</P>
<P>
 AKI AKAIKE 
</P>
<P>
 Gardena 
</P>
