<TEXT>
<P>
 A man police say strangled neighbors and women he worked with during a killing 
spree that lasted nearly two years was charged Sunday with 10 counts of murder. 
</P>
<P>
 Henry Louis Wallace, 28, was arrested Feb. 4 after a theft at a shopping mall 
but was released.He was arrested again Saturday, and police said four of the 10 
