mothers.Comparative Rates: 
</P>
<P>
 There are 12 counties in California with higher rates of AIDS than Orange 
County. The highest: San Francisco County, with 2,190 per 100,000 residents. 
Here's how Southern California counties compare to one another and to the 
state. Cumulative cases per 100,000 residents, 1981-1993: 
</P>
<P>
