<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE STYLE FILES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Six Ways of Looking at Fashion 
</P>
<P>
 TODAY: The Pictures 
</P>
<P>
 NEXT: The Places 
</P>
<P>
 PHOTOGRAPHER: Al Seib 
</P>
<P>
 ART DIRECTOR: Tracy Crowe 
</P>
