CLARIFICATION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 BOWERS MUSEUM -- A review March 1 of an exhibit at the Bowers Museum of 
Cultural Art in Santa Ana made an inaccurate reference to the curatorial staff 
there. The staff consists of Paul Apodaca, curator of Native American and folk 
art, and Armand Labbe, director of collections and research. There is no fine 
art curator on the staff. 
</P>
